Apache Status Plugin
======================

Created by Hampton Catlin
Modifications and documentation by Josh Nichols and Jesse Newland

Overview
--------

Reports data collected from from apache2ctl:

 * Idle workers
 * Requests being handled
 * Apache reserved memory size
 * Requests/second
 * Kilobytes/seconds
 * Bytes/request

Configuration
-------------

apache2ctl must be installed. You can specify a custom path to apache2ctl if necessary.

Known limitations
-----------------

 * not all values are reported from `apache2ctl status` yet